player.description:
|Fin is still figuring out how to fight, but he's an expert when it comes to buffs and debuffs.
His kind heart is searching for its place in this world.

enter.message: |There should be a VOC-Library to try them out for free... I'd be there all day, everyday.

player.description:
|In contrast to literally anybody else, Spark gets heated up after getting stunned.
Her soul was made for combat!

|This young Noise Hunter is a great fighter until his energy starts to run out.
Luckily travelling in exile has made him sturdy.

|The loyal Punks always go all out\u2026 and beyond!
They thrive in clutch which helps when fighting a company as powerful as Azure Shield.

|The leader of Crimson Force, with coffee in her veins and a fire in her heart.
She\u2019s strongest when fighting her enemies head on.
|AV.atar could be anyone really. Who hides behind the helmet? You decide.

|Once the Agents get into the groove, their attacks keep getting stronger and stronger!
They respect Del and will do anything to fulfil her plans.

|Azure Shields boss prefers to take a step back in fights and attack from afar.
She is the most strategic fighter in all of Anikka.

enter.message: |That's an interesting one. I'd like to talk to the developer one day.

player.description: |Azure Shield's vice commander crushes any obstacle in Del's way. His mighty crystal influences anyone who has come in contact with his attacks.

|Will shoot anyone, while wearing a smile on its face.
Wait\u2026 is that just a smile drawn on a sticky note? Who would fall for that???
|This Noise likes to wait for its prey to turn it\u2019s back\u2026 don\u2019t ever sit on it.
|This mysterious little blobs goo allows it to fluently travel between panels and even fix them!
|Oozing all over the place, this monstrous creature thrives on the planet burning.

|These aggressive Noises heat up once they\u2019re low on HP.
Their devious nature makes for an explosive combatant.
|One of the strongest and most regal Noises out there\u2026 until it gets hit by an electric attack and turns into a miserable puddle.
|Don\u2019t pet these rascals. They take it like no problem, but they\u2019ll shock ya. Also don\u2019t attack them with electro-attacks... just avoid them in general.

|This easy going reptile makes sure to plant a seed whenever it can. But be careful!
Those seeds can turn into dangerous log launches.
|Tri-Wings unique fighting skill allows it to re-charge all its attacks every few seconds. It also moves like it\u2019s walking through life in a straight line.
|This deinty space traveller uses her stack ability to empower a VOC when its used over and over! Her Infinity Slash follows its target to the end of the universe!
|Jeremy's cool attitude and way with the guitar impresses anyone that crosses his path! With his unique ultra Voc Jeremy makes every battle a special occasion.
